Fun Kids Game- Our customers say this Family Card Game is so much fun that you will LAUGH UNTIL YOU CRY! Kids and Adults- say that this game is A BLAST TO PLAY for everyone of all ages. It’s Easy to Play. Simple to set up.
Award Winning Gift For Boys And Girls- Moms Choice Award For Excellence- The perfect gift for your 6-12 year old son, daughter, niece or nephew and grandkids/grandchildren. Combining the super popular card game fundamentals of Cards Against Humanity and Apples to Apples into one hilarious party game. Contains age appropriate content for a true family card game experience that you can enjoy playing on Family Game Night.
What’s In The Box- The card game includes 465 Top Quality Cards-95 Question Cards-350 Answer Cards-10 Random Task Cards-10 Blank Cards but most of all it includes LOTS OF FUN! Priced Right for all Families to afford.
Friends and Family Lots Of Laughs-We guarantee that you will have so much fun and laughter playing Kids Create Absurdity, that if you do not like it just send it back for a full refund.
Christmas Stocking Stuffer- Kids Create Absurdity is a great choice to give as a gift this Christmas or to use as a stocking stuffer.
